### Setup .env file

```js
PORT=...
PRO_DB_HOST=localhost
PRO_DB_PORT=27017
PRO_DB_NAME=...
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=...
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=...
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=...
```

### Build the app

```shell
npm run build
```

### Start the app

```shell
npm start
```
